jobs.title: Software Engineer
jobs.description: As an engineer on the Visual Studio Team Services team in Raleigh, NC you'll be part of an 8-12 person agile team working together to ship weekly updates to Visual Studio Team Services and the products around it

jobs.title: UX / UI Designer
jobs.description: We are looking for a user-experience (UX) designer able to understand our business requirements and any technical limitations, as well as be responsible for conceiving and conducting user research, interviews and surveys, and translating them into sitemaps, user flows, customer journey maps, wireframes, mockups and prototypes. The UX designer will also be expected to design the overall functionality of the product, and in order to ensure a great user experience, iterate upon it in accordance with user-testing

jobs.title: Mobile Application Developer
jobs.description: The Nike+ Apps team is seeking a Senior iOS Engineer to join us in developing premium native experiences for our consumers. In this role, you will deliver well designed, highly testable, and resilient applications and/or POCs. You will also be instrumental in exploring new platforms, technologies, and partnerships with industry leaders. The successful candidate is both deeply experienced with iOS development and loves bleeding edge technology outside of the iOS ecosystem.
